-- Barclays Africa sees single-digit loan growth continuing 
-- By Helen Nyambura-Mwaura
-- Wed Jul 30, 2014 04:11AM EDT
-- None



JOHANNESBURG, July 30 (Reuters) - Barclays Africa Group <BGAJ.J> sees "mid single digit" loan growth continuing, its deputy chief executive said on Wednesday, reflecting its more cautious stance to writing new business.

